858
00:37:50,020 --> 00:37:50,860
in Hankou.

859
00:37:51,260 --> 00:37:52,260
How about Hankou?

860
00:37:52,260 --> 00:37:52,940
Okay.

861
00:37:52,940 --> 00:37:54,580
You can open them wherever you want.

862
00:37:54,860 --> 00:37:57,060
And then in Chengdu.

863
00:37:57,860 --> 00:37:59,220
Great! Chengdu's perfect.

864
00:38:00,460 --> 00:38:03,620
We'll expand our stores

865
00:38:04,820 --> 00:38:06,300
across the entire country!

866
00:38:07,260 --> 00:38:08,100
One city at a time.

867
00:38:08,100 --> 00:38:09,500
Exactly, step by step.

868
00:38:10,740 --> 00:38:11,540
First, conquer Shanghai.

869
00:38:11,540 --> 00:38:12,420
We'll have to give it our all!

870
00:38:23,060 --> 00:38:24,100
Why has she been crying

871
00:38:24,100 --> 00:38:25,700
