872
00:38:25,940 --> 00:38:27,140
Doesn't want me to leave.

873
00:38:27,340 --> 00:38:27,980
Xuan,

874
00:38:28,260 --> 00:38:29,340
- he will be back very soon.
- Alright now.

875
00:38:29,340 --> 00:38:29,780
Right.

876
00:38:30,020 --> 00:38:32,500
I'll bring you tasty treats.
Be a good child.

877
00:38:32,980 --> 00:38:34,420
When will you be back?

878
00:38:35,580 --> 00:38:37,660
Father wants to collect
the remaining payment

879
00:38:37,860 --> 00:38:40,180
and connect the medicine traders
in Shanxi.

880
00:38:40,180 --> 00:38:41,580
It'll take at least half a month.

881
00:38:43,060 --> 00:38:45,580
Alright. You'll make it
to our branch's opening.

882
00:38:46,380 --> 00:38:48,780
When I return,
we'll unveil the signboard together.

883
00:38:49,580 --> 00:38:52,100
We finally have our own business.

884
00:38:53,460 --> 00:38:54,140
Shaohua,

885
00:38:54,820 --> 00:38:56,700
you've truly endured so much
over these past few years.

886
00:38:57,220 --> 00:38:58,500
Why do you say that?

887
00:38:59,260 --> 00:38:59,900
Look,

888
00:38:59,900 --> 00:39:01,820
you always wanted
to explore the outside world,

889
00:39:02,100 --> 00:39:03,500
to build something of your own.

890
00:39:03,980 --> 00:39:05,860
Yet it took till now,
till this very day.

891
00:39:07,460 --> 00:39:09,180
Everything is turning out
quite well now.

892
00:39:09,820 --> 00:39:11,180
As long as we put in the effort,

893
00:39:11,660 --> 00:39:12,980
what's destined to arrive

894
00:39:13,660 --> 00:39:14,900
will find its way to us.

895
00:39:15,060 --> 00:39:17,580
Be careful on your journey.

896
00:39:17,780 --> 00:39:18,740
Don't worry.

897
00:39:18,740 --> 00:39:20,700
Dashun will travel with me.

898
00:39:21,260 --> 00:39:23,060
Besides, Wei Donglai's clerks

899
00:39:23,060 --> 00:39:25,100
are also heading to Shanxi on business.

900
00:39:25,100 --> 00:39:26,820
There'll be four or five of us
along the way.

901
00:39:26,820 --> 00:39:28,420
Nothing untoward will happen.

902
00:39:28,620 --> 00:39:30,260
Alright, just stay home and take care.

903
00:39:30,660 --> 00:39:31,220
Mr. Chen.

904
00:39:31,220 --> 00:39:31,700
Okay.

905
00:39:31,700 --> 00:39:34,500
♪I hold your hand, never to leave♪

906
00:39:37,940 --> 00:39:39,660
Where's the food for the journey?

907
00:39:39,660 --> 00:39:42,460
♪Time flows quietly, unnoticed♪

908
00:39:43,260 --> 00:39:43,940
I'm leaving.

909
00:39:44,060 --> 00:39:48,540
♪Drifting eastward, never pausing♪

910
00:39:48,540 --> 00:39:49,340
Dashun,

911
00:39:51,700 --> 00:39:52,580
I'll wait for you to come back.

912
00:39:52,620 --> 00:39:56,580
♪Clouds outside the window disperse
and gather, and spring comes and leaves♪

913
00:39:58,180 --> 00:40:00,580
♪Now and in the past,
I walk beside you evermore♪

914
00:40:00,620 --> 00:40:01,540
Wait for me.

915
00:40:04,460 --> 00:40:12,100
♪I vow to dedicate my life
to guarding only you♪

916
00:40:12,860 --> 00:40:15,620
♪Shielding you from every storm♪

917
00:40:15,660 --> 00:40:16,620
Be careful on the way.

918
00:40:18,380 --> 00:40:19,580
Be careful on the way.

919
00:40:19,620 --> 00:40:22,500
♪My heart is a city,
built solely to protect you♪

920
00:40:22,540 --> 00:40:23,180
Go.

921
00:40:23,940 --> 00:40:24,660
Go.

922
00:40:26,660 --> 00:40:33,180
