932
00:41:21,900 --> 00:41:23,020
these past few days!

933
00:41:26,020 --> 00:41:26,700
I'm so worried.

934
00:41:28,020 --> 00:41:28,900
Look,

935
00:41:29,020 --> 00:41:30,540
since you're uneasy,

936
00:41:30,580 --> 00:41:32,460
