at Wei Donglai's place.

937
00:41:35,580 --> 00:41:36,860
No tears, Xuan.

938
00:41:36,860 --> 00:41:38,540
I'm right here. Shh, hush now.

939
00:41:39,060 --> 00:41:40,180
Everything is going to be fine.

940
00:41:40,420 --> 00:41:41,900
Father will be home in just a few days

941
00:41:43,260 --> 00:41:45,420
