956
00:42:27,380 --> 00:42:28,540
Hard to say.

957
00:42:36,180 --> 00:42:37,140
The plague?

958
00:42:38,740 --> 00:42:39,820
Your father and Dashun…

959
00:42:40,020 --> 00:42:40,740
Mother,

960
